item.title: 【HD Live Performances】WEB-RiP - Charlotte Perrelli, Carola, Conchita Wurst - Waterloo (Live at Eurovision Song Contest 2024) [1080p, AAC]
item.description:
Charlotte Perrelli, Carola & Conchita Wurst perform Abba's 1974 winning Eurovision hit "Waterloo" live at Eurovision Song Contest 2024 in Malmö, Sweden, 11.05.2024.
Web-Rip from the stream at Eurovision.de (German broadcaster), not the best but it does the job.
1080p with 320 kb/s AAC Audio.

Enjoy ;)
